{"text_id":168369,"tokens":["In"," today","'","s"," complex"," and"," rapidly"," changing"," world",","," making"," informed"," decisions"," and"," solving"," problems"," effectively"," is"," essential"," for"," success"," in"," both"," personal"," and"," professional"," life","."," While"," some"," people"," may"," prefer"," to"," rely"," on"," their"," own"," judgment"," and"," experience",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," can"," provide"," several"," benefits"," that"," can"," lead"," to"," better"," outcomes","."," In"," this"," essay",","," I"," will"," argue"," that"," seeking"," advice"," from"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," people"," can"," offer"," fresh"," perspectives",","," challenge"," assumptions",","," reduce"," biases",","," and"," increase"," the"," likelihood"," of"," making"," a"," well","-","informed"," decision",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," primary"," benefits"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," is"," that"," it"," can"," provide"," fresh"," perspectives"," on"," a"," problem"," or"," decision","."," When"," faced"," with"," a"," challenging"," situation",","," it"," is"," easy"," to"," become"," fix","ated"," on"," a"," particular"," solution"," or"," approach",","," often"," due"," to"," our"," own"," biases"," and"," assumptions","."," By"," consulting"," with"," others",","," we"," can"," expose"," ourselves"," to"," new"," ideas"," and"," ways"," of"," thinking"," that"," we"," may"," not"," have"," considered"," on"," our"," own","."," This"," can"," help"," us"," to"," see"," the"," problem"," from"," different"," angles"," and"," identify"," creative"," solutions"," that"," we"," may"," have"," overlooked",".","\n\n","Another"," advantage"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," is"," that"," it"," can"," challenge"," our"," assumptions"," and"," help"," us"," to"," identify"," potential"," biases","."," When"," we"," are"," deeply"," involved"," in"," a"," problem"," or"," decision",","," it"," can"," be"," difficult"," to"," recognize"," our"," own"," blind"," spots"," and"," limitations","."," By"," gathering"," input"," from"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," people",","," we"," can"," benefit"," from"," their"," unique"," experiences",","," knowledge",","," and"," insights",","," which"," can"," help"," us"," to"," see"," things"," from"," a"," different"," perspective","."," This"," can"," lead"," to"," a"," more"," comprehensive"," understanding"," of"," the"," issue"," at"," hand"," and"," a"," more"," objective"," assessment"," of"," the"," available"," options",".","\n\n","Moreover",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," can"," also"," help"," to"," reduce"," the"," risk"," of"," group","think"," and"," promote"," more"," effective"," decision","-","making","."," Group","think"," is"," a"," phenomenon"," that"," occurs"," when"," a"," group"," of"," people",","," often"," in"," a"," leadership"," role",","," come"," to"," a"," consensus"," without"," critically"," evaluating"," the"," available"," options","."," This"," can"," lead"," to"," poor"," decision","-","making",","," as"," the"," group"," may"," ignore"," important"," considerations"," or"," fail"," to"," consider"," alternative"," viewpoints","."," By"," seeking"," advice"," from"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," people",","," we"," can"," mitigate"," the"," risk"," of"," group","think"," and"," ensure"," that"," all"," relevant"," factors"," are"," considered",".","\n\n","In"," addition",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," can"," also"," increase"," our"," confidence"," in"," the"," decision","-","making"," process","."," When"," we"," make"," important"," decisions"," or"," solve"," complex"," problems"," on"," our"," own",","," it"," can"," be"," challenging"," to"," have"," complete"," confidence"," in"," the"," outcome","."," However",","," by"," gathering"," input"," from"," a"," variety"," of"," sources",","," we"," can"," increase"," our"," confidence"," that"," we"," have"," considered"," all"," relevant"," factors"," and"," thoroughly"," evaluated"," the"," available"," options","."," This"," can"," help"," us"," to"," feel"," more"," secure"," in"," our"," decisions",","," even"," in"," the"," face"," of"," uncertainty",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," can"," help"," to"," build"," trust"," and"," strengthen"," relationships","."," By"," demonstrating"," a"," willingness"," to"," listen"," to"," others"," and"," consider"," their"," opinions",","," we"," can"," foster"," a"," culture"," of"," collaboration"," and"," inclu","sivity","."," This"," can"," help"," to"," build"," trust"," and"," strengthen"," relationships",","," both"," within"," our"," personal"," and"," professional"," networks","."," Additionally",","," by"," seeking"," advice"," from"," others",","," we"," are"," also"," demonstrating"," that"," we"," value"," their"," expertise"," and"," insights",","," which"," can"," help"," to"," build"," their"," confidence"," and"," engagement"," in"," the"," decision","-","making"," process",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," when"," faced"," with"," a"," problem"," or"," decision"," can"," offer"," several"," benefits"," that"," can"," lead"," to"," better"," outcomes","."," By"," providing"," fresh"," perspectives",","," challenging"," assumptions",","," reducing"," biases",","," increasing"," confidence",","," and"," building"," trust",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," people"," can"," help"," us"," to"," make"," well","-","informed"," decisions"," and"," solve"," complex"," problems"," effectively","."," As"," leaders",","," it"," is"," essential"," to"," recognize"," the"," value"," of"," diversity"," and"," inclu","sivity"," in"," the"," decision","-","making"," process"," and"," to"," cultivate"," a"," culture"," of"," collaboration"," and"," openness","."," By"," doing"," so",","," we"," can"," leverage"," the"," collective"," wisdom"," and"," expertise"," of"," our"," networks"," to"," achieve"," our"," goals"," and"," succeed"," in"," today","'","s"," rapidly"," changing"," world","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}